{"tid":2235021,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聾啞囚犯涉襲懲教罪名不成立 官指未能確定是否蓄意施襲","createTime":"2020-10-08T10:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T00:43:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f634564d1bf417c7e03ae0ab088468313f5dde9f","tid":2235021,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:48:52.000Z","msg":"駐守赤柱監獄的懲教助理今年初向一名聾啞囚犯退回郵費不足的信件，其間聲稱遭該囚犯抓傷前臂，涉案囚犯被控襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，案件早前在東區裁判法院審結。裁判官崔美霞今裁決時，質疑事主以不同字詞形容被告舉動，而現場片段也無法反映二人完整的交流過程，無法確定被告是否蓄意施襲，故裁定被告罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/DO7DHJZEMNFDTG5XZ23ND7NIOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FDO7DHJZEMNFDTG5XZ23ND7NIOY%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=6dd64bc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201008%2FDO7DHJZEMNFDTG5XZ23ND7NIOY%2F&h=0823a06c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201008/DO7DHJZEMNFDTG5XZ23ND7NIOY/</a>"},{"pid":"8fd2837d2fdd743401798000c25cdb23edea7e49","tid":2235021,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c053f9190c565ce25828bbe2aa26891e56d9f498","tid":2235021,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:53:59.000Z","msg":"聾啞手足？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd33a71e52ab171bc36866e9ab11c9a630294670","tid":2235021,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T10:57:03.000Z","msg":